ses%20in%20other%20states%2C%20the%20company%20went%20through%20ridiculous%20contortions%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-dont-pay-federal-income-taxes-amazon-gm-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20avoid%20establishing%20a%20sales%20tax%20%26quot%3Bnexus%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20those%20other%20states%2C%20because%20that%20would%20have%20meant%20customers%20would%20have%20had%20to%20pay%20an%20extra%207%25%20or%20more%20on%20all%20their%20purchases%2C%20crushing%20Amazon's%20sales%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Bezos%20is%20selling%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20Amazon%20stock%20every%20year%2C%20and%20he's%20on%20the%20move%20again.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kiplinger.com%2Ftaxes%2Fwashington-state-capital-gains-tax%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20state%20recently%20introduced%20a%207%25%20capital%20gains%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20deemed%20constitutional%20only%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20Now%2C%20he's%20off%20to%20Miami%20which%20has%20no%20capital%20gains%20tax%2C%20and%20is%20known%20for%20being%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20tax-avoidant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20do%20some%20simple%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20has%20sold%20about%202.1%20million%20Amazon%20shares%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.aboutamazon.com%2Fsec-filings%2Fsec-filings-details%2Fdefault.aspx%3FFilingId%3D16361618%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%20filings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famzn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20traded%20between%20%2485%20and%20%24138%20per%20share%20this%20year%2C%20so%20let's%20say%20just%20for%20illustrative%20purposes%20that%20he%20sold%20at%20an%20average%20price%20of%20%24100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20%24210%20million%2C%20some%20of%20which%20is%20likely%20capital%20gains.%20Washington%20state%20now%20levies%20a%207%25%20capital%20gains%20tax.%20There%20are%20some%20exemptions%2C%20but%20only%20for%20the%20first%20first%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20in%20gains%20each%20year.%20So%20that%20would%20theoretically%20mean%20that%20Bezos%20could%20have%20owed%20millions%20in%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20his%20Amazon%20stock%20sales%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20those%20SEC%20filings%2C%20Bezos%20still%20owns%20990%20million%20Amazon%20shares.%20At%20today's%20stock%20price%2C%20that's%20worth%20about%20%24137%20billion.%20Put%20a%207%25%20tax%20on%20that%2C%20and%20the%20bill%20could%20be%20in%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20billionaires%20often%20have%20most%20of%20their%20wealth%20tied%20up%20in%20stock.%20They%20don't%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20income%20tax%2C%20but%20they%20do%20focus%20a%20lot%20on%20capital%20gains%20tax.%20Bezos%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20Amazon%20stock%20but%20also%20has%20made%20a%20number%20of%20other%20investments%20over%20the%20years.%20Those%20holdings%20will%20probably%20be%20exposed%20to%20capital%20gains%20tax%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20move%20to%20Miami%20to%20save%20that%20much%3F%20I%20would.%20Your%20mother%20would%20call%20it%20just%20good%20sense.%20Oh%2C%20and%20call%20your%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-move-miami-parents-avoid-taxes-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699040785000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654511ddb788914e554fba49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-move-miami-parents-avoid-taxes-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeff%20Bezos%20is%20moving%20from%20Seattle%20to%20Miami%20with%20fianc%C3%A9%20Lauren%20Sanchez.%20What%20loving%20son%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20be%20near%20his%20parents%20in%20their%20golden%20years%2C%20especially%2