ostly%20as%20the%20urban%20fight%20intensifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20%26quot%3Bare%20encircling%20Gaza%20City%20from%20the%20air%2C%20the%20land%2C%20and%20the%20sea%2C%26quot%3B%20Rear%20Adm.%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20Friday.%20He%20said%20Israeli%20troops%20are%20%26quot%3Badvancing%20in%20battles%2C%26quot%3B%20destroying%20Hamas%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20killing%20militants%2C%20as%20well%20as%20eliminating%20tunnels%20belonging%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20open-source%20intelligence%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWar_Mapper%2Fstatus%2F1720154499619135581%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20positional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Firan-update-november-2-2023%5C%22%3Emapping%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%20monitoring%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20IDF%20has%20approached%20the%20city%20along%20multiple%20axes.%20Israeli%20forces%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20northeast%20and%20northwest%20corners%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20to%20the%20south%2C%20the%20IDF%20has%20effectively%20severed%20the%20strip%20into%20two%20halves%20by%20driving%20a%20wedge%20that%20runs%20from%20the%20border%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20repeatedly%20urged%20the%20population%20of%20northern%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20some%201%20million%20people%2C%20and%20where%20Gaza%20City%20is%20located%20%E2%80%94%20to%20evacuate%20to%20the%20south%20both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-ground-invasion-gaza-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%3Eexpanded%20ground%20offensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20in%20late%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20several%20days%2C%20as%20Israeli%20forces%20closed%20in%20on%20Gaza%20City%2C%20they%20have%20faced%20an%20array%20of%20different%20threats%20from%20Hamas%20while%20engaging%20in%20combat%20inside%20the%20enclave.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20IDF%20has%20said%2C%20are%20anti-tank%20missiles%2C%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%20(IEDs)%2C%20grenades%20thrown%20at%20troops%2C%20and%20ambushes%20conducted%20by%20way%20of%20the%20militant%20group's%20notorious%20underground%20tunnel%20network.%20The%20military%20has%20released%20photographs%20and%20videos%20showing%20infantry%20and%20armor%20operating%20in%20unspecified%20locations%20throughout%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20military%20armor%20inside%20Gaza.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654544b83cc84b4dfafc44ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20military%20armor%20operating%20inside%20Gaza.%3Cp%3EIDF%20via%20Telegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20published%20a%20handful%20videos%20to%20social%20media%20that%20show%20intense%20gun%20battles%2C%20rocket%20fire%2C%20and%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20troops%20and%20heavy%20armor.%20Insider%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20immediately%20verify%20all%20of%20the%20footage.%20So%20far%2C%20around%20two%20dozen%20Israeli%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20unclear%20number%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20%E2%80%94%20have%20reportedly%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-11-03%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Ffive-additional-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation%2F0000018b-948a-db7e-af9b-ffcbbc660000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20ground%20invasion.%20With%20Gaza%20City%20now%20effectively%20encircled%20and%20a%20deeper%20assault%20on%20it%20appearing%20imminent%2C%20the%20casualty%20figures%20could%20continue%20to%20rise.%