%20Telangana%20Assembly%20Polls%2C%20Offers%20Support%20to%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03224845%2FF3yw807aoAA7aij.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20(YSRTP)%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Rajashekar%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Y.S.%20Sharmila%2C%20has%20announced%20its%20decision%20to%20not%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections.%20The%20YSRTP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20pulling%20out%20of%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20top%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20YSRTP%20has%20expressed%20its%20unconditional%20support%20to%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20371px)%2085vw%2C%20371px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22371%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharmila%2C%20who%20had%20huddled%20with%20party%20leaders%20earlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20noted%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20like-minded%20parties%20put%20up%20a%20joint%20fight%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmisrule%E2%80%9D%20of%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR).%20According%20to%20Sharmila%2C%20since%20Congress%20stands%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%2C%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20would%20dent%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharmila%20also%20based%20her%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20she%20was%20the%20true%20heir%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20her%20father%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20who%20steered%20Congress%20to%20power%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20twice%20in%202004%20and%202009.%20So%2C%20she%20said%20she%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20contributing%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20Congress%20by%20splitting%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRTP%20party%20has%20done%20a%20volte-face%20in%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20contest%20as%20it%20had%20threatened%20to%20contest%20in%20all%20119%20Assembly%20constituencies%20of%20Telangana%20only%20a%20fortnight%20ago.%20Sharmila%20had%20then%20said%20the%20party%20waited%20long%20enough%20expecting%20a%20favourable%20response%20from%20Congress%20to%20the%20YSRTP%E2%80%99s%20merger%20after%20personally%20taking%20it%20up%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Delhi%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20On%20the%20suggestion%20of%20Gandhis%2C%20she%20had%20waited%20enough%20but%20there%20was%20no%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20to%20Delhi%20by%20Sharmila%20and%20her%20husband%20Anil%20was%20preceded%20by%20hectic%20preparations%20by%20the%20YSR%20party%20to%20contest%20elections%20with%20the%20sole%20aim%20of%20defeating%20the%20ruling%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti.%20Sharmila%20said%20she%20herself%20would%20contest%20from%20the%20Palair%20constituency%20in%20the%20Khammam%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharmila%20was%20not%20known%20to%20be%20nursing%20political%20ambitions%20until%20serious%20differences%20arose%20with%20her%20brother%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Y.%20S.%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20three%20years%20ago.%20She%20organised%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Khammam%20in%202021%20to%20announce%20her%20plans%20to%20enter%20public%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%202%20the%20same%20year%2C%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20party%20was%20launched%20in%20Hyderabad.%20This%20was%20immediately%20followed%20by%20a%20dinner%20meeting%20hosted%20by%20her%20mother%20Vijayamma%20for%20colleagues%20of%20her%20late%20husband%20across%20parties%20to%20seek%20blessings%20for%20Sharmila.%20Since%20many%20leaders%20who%20worked%20with%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20were%20in%20the%20present%20ruling%20party%20in%20Telangana%20and%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified%20with%20her%2C%20all%20notable%20personalities%20gave%20it%20a%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharmila%20shot%20to%20fame%20with%20her%203%2C100%20km%20padayatra%20in%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20when%20Jagan%20was%20in%20jail%20in%20a%20disproportionate%20assets%20case%20in%202012-13.%20She%20also%20campaigned%20for%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20party%20of%20Jagan%20in%20his%20absence%20on%20account%20of%20imprisonment%20in%20byelections%20of%20AP.%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20party%20then%20won%2015%20out%20of%2018%20Assembly%20constituencies%20and%20Nellore%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20went%20to%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20confining%20herself%20to%20home%20for%20five%20years%20on%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20release%20from%20jail%2C%20she%20again%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20in%20elections%20to%20the%20AP%20Assembly%20in%202019%20that%20saw%20the%20rout%20of%20TDP%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20then%20that%20differences%20arose%20in%20the%20family%20with%20Sharmila%20reportedly%20demanding%20her%20share%20in%20the%20cake%20after%20the%20party%20formed%20government%20in%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20reported%20that%20Sharmila%20decided%20to%20be%20a%20power%20centre%20herself%2C%20but%20in%20Telangana%20when%20she%20fell%20out%20with%20Jagan.%20She%20then%20undertook%20a%203%2C800%20km%20padayatra%20in%20Telangana%2C%20her%20second%20walkathon%2C%20for%20over%20a%20year%20from%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20received%20a%20good%20response%20from%20the%20public%20but%20it%20was%20stopped%20by%20the%20government%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20occasions%20on%20grounds%20of%20provocative%20speeches%20against%20the%20chief%20minister.%20She%20resumed%20the%20yatra%20with%20conditional%20permission%20given%20by%20the%20court%20but%20was%20forced%20to%20terminate%20it%20once%20more%20following%20her%20arrest%20by%20police%20in%20Mahbubabad%20last%20year.%20Ever%20since%2C%20she%20had%20voiced%20her%20intention%20to%20contest%20from%20Palair%20where%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20former%20Khammam%20MP%20Ponguleti%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20for%20the%20current%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699032114000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03224845%2FF3yw807aoAA7aij.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%20a%20fortnight%20ago%2C%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20contest%20across%20the%20state%20after%20its%20merger%20talks%20with%20Congress%20broke%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jung%20Kook's%20Golden%3A%20BTS%20star%20crowned%20'pop%20king'%20by%20critics%20thanks%20to%20solo%20album%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699031289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2A31%2Fproduction%2F_131610801_gettyimages-1698949137.jpg%22%2C%22or