ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjk-paper-posts-6-8-fall-in-q2-profit-on-lower-demand-higher-input-costs-123110300991_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjk-paper-posts-6-8-fall-in-q2-profit-on-lower-demand-higher-input-costs-123110300991_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Annual%20Report%20on%20Digital%20Labour%20Platforms%20Shows%20Worker%20Pay%20Is%20Largely%20Below%20Living%20Wage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F11165805%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-4.57.43-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Zero%20of%20the%2012%20digital%20labour%20platforms%20evaluated%20in%20the%20Fairwork%20India%202023%20report%20showed%20evidence%20of%20providing%20their%20workers%20with%20a%20living%20wage.%20Only%20three%20of%20the%2012%20%E2%80%94%20bigbasket%2C%20Flipkart%20and%20Urban%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20ensured%20the%20local%20minimum%20wage%20after%20work-related%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20no%20platform%20to%20ensure%20fair%20representation%20for%20their%20workers%2C%20meaning%20platforms%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20process%20through%20which%20workers%20could%20express%20their%20voices%20collectively%2C%20such%20as%20through%20recognised%20trade%20unions%20or%20collective%20bodies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRepresentation%20through%20a%20collective%20body%20or%20trade%20union%20is%20a%20vital%20dimension%20of%20fairness%20at%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20disconcerting%20that%20despite%20the%20rise%20in%20platform%20worker%20collectivisation%20across%20the%20country%2C%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20there%20was%20insufficient%20evidence%20from%20any%20platform%20that%20showed%20a%20willingness%20to%20recognise%20a%20collective%20body%20of%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFairwork%20evaluated%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20gig%20workers%20at%20Amazon%20Flex%2C%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Dunzo%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20Ola%2C%20Porter%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Uber%2C%20Urban%20Company%2C%20Zepto%20and%20Zomato%20using%20five%20principles%3A%20fair%20pay%2C%20fair%20conditions%2C%20fair%20contracts%2C%20fair%20management%20and%20fair%20representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20desk%20research%20and%20359%20worker%20interviews%20across%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Kochi%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20platforms%20were%20graded%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%20Under%20each%20principle%2C%20companies%20could%20receive%20two%20points.%20This%20year%2C%20no%20platform%20scored%20higher%20than%20six%20points.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20conditions%2C%2010%20platforms%20received%20the%20first%20point%20for%20%E2%80%9Cproviding%20adequate%20safety%20equipment%20and%20periodic%20safety%20training%20to%20their%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20A%20second%20point%20was%20given%20to%20five%20platforms%20for%20providing%20workers%20with%20accident%20insurance%20coverage%20at%20no%20additional%20cost%2C%20compensating%20workers%20for%20income%20lost%20due%20to%20medical%20leave%20and%20for%20ensuring%20that%20workers%E2%80%99%20standing%20was%20not%20negatively%20affected%20after%20returning%20to%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20contracts%2C%20seven%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Dunzo%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Urban%20Company%2C%20Zepto%20and%20Zomato%20%E2%80%94%20were%20awarded%20the%20first%20point%20for%20ensuring%20their%20contracts%20were%20accessible%20and%20comprehensible%2C%20and%20for%20having%20a%20protocol%20for%20data%20protection%20and%20management.%20Five%20met%20the%20requirements%20for%20the%20second%20point%20that%20required%20more%20transparent%20and%20clarifying%20language%20in%20worker%20contracts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20management%2C%20Amazon%20Flex%2C%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20and%20Zomato%20were%20awarded%20the%20first%20point%20for%20providing%20due%20process%20in%20decisions%20affecting%20workers%20and%20maintaining%20channels%20for%20workers%20to%20appeal%20disciplinary%20actions.%20Only%20BluSmart%20and%20Swiggy%20received%20a%20second%20point%20for%20regulating%20external%20audits%20to%20check%20for%20biases%20in%20how%20work%20is%20allocated%20among%20workers%20and%20for%20adopting%20anti-discrimination%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20report%20focuses%20on%20a%20different%20theme.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20theme%20was%20discrimination%20and%20alienation%20felt%20by%20platform%20workers.%20Fairwork%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20provisions%20in%20place%20for%20fair%20representation%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20inability%20to%20influence%20how%20platforms%20address%20collective%20issues%20has%20contributed%20to%20alienation%20or%20estrangement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFairwork%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20alienation%20is%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20the%20discrimination%20that%20platform%20workers%20face%20due%20to%20social%20identities%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20a%20national%20scale%2C%20Fairwork%20said%202023%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmilestone%20year%20for%20platform%20workers%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20This%20year%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Platform%20Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare)%20Act%2C%202023%20was%20passed%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eregulates%20the%20engagement%20of%20platform-based%20gig%20workers%20and%20aims%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20social%20security%20and%20other%20benefits.%20The%20legislation%20came%20after%20years%20of%20platform%20workers%20organizing%20for%20their%20rights%20and%20raising%20claims%20with%20the%20State.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20rules%20for%20implementing%20the%20Rajasthan%20Act%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20framed%2C%20the%20act%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20providing%20social%20security%20to%20platform%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20also%20called%20to%20ensure%20%E2%80%9Cadequate%20social%20protection%20and%20decent%20working%20conditions%20for%20gig%20and%20platform%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20year%20that%20has%20seen%20the%20formulation%20of%20a%20significant%20regulation%20based%20on%20inputs%20from%20workers%2C%20we%20hope%20that%20highlighting%20the%20experiences%20of%20workers%20will%20point%20to%20the%20structural%20changes%20that%20platforms%2C%20consumers%20and%20the%20State%20alike%20will%20need%20to%20undertake%20if%20the%20platform%20economy%20is%20to%20offer%20its%20workers%20decent%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Professors%20Balaji%20Parthasarathy%20and%20Janaki%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%20principal%20investigators%20of%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20interviewing%20workers%2C%20the%20Fairwork%20India%202023%20report%20included%20a%20survey%20of%20963%20consumers%20across%20the%2012%20platforms%20to%20gauge%20consumer%20awareness%20of%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20platform%20workers.%20Fairwork%20said%20in%20the%20largest%20cities%20surveyed%2C%20there%20was%20significant%20support%20for%20bringing%20change%20to%20working%20conditions%20in%20the%20platform%20economy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsumers%20can%20use%20these%20scores%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20which%20platforms%20to%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20scores%20can%20serve%20as%20additional%20resources%20for%20collective%20worker%20bodies%20when%20they%20raise%20demands.%20We%20also%20hope%20that%20the%20findings%20of%20this%20report%20will%20provide%20regulators%20with%20a%20basis%20to%20formulate%20policies%20for%20the%20platform%20economy%20in%20consultation%20with%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20workers%2C%20platforms%20and%20venture%20capitalists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699016437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F11165805%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-4.57.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fannual-report-on-digital-labour-platforms-shows-worker-pay-is-largely-below-living-wage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fairwork%20India%20has%20released%20its%205th%20annual%20study%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20discrimination%20and%20alienation%20felt%20by%20platform%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fannual-report-on-digital-labour-platforms-shows-worker-pay-is-largely-below-living-wage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20casts%20a%20spell%20in%20a%20daring%20Rs%201%20lakh%20mini-dress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699015164000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104946441%2Cimgsize-34054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-casts-a-spell-in-a-daring-rs-1-lakh-mini-dress-with-a-plunging-neckline-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104946441.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104946441.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20is%20seen%20in%20a%20strapless%20mini%20dress%20featuri