n-death-count%5C%22%3Ehas%20cast%20doubt%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20overall%20death%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20of%20the%20UNRWA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fun-says-gaza-health-ministry-death-tolls-in-previous-wars%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20death%20count%20is%20reliably%20accurate%2C%20Lee%20gave%20several%20reasons%20for%20accepting%20the%20death%20count%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Hamas%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20in%20Gaza.%20It%20aligns%20with%20the%20death%20counts%20from%20earlier%20Hamas-Israel%20wars%2C%20although%2C%20in%20overall%20terms%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20much%20greater%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELee%20gave%20graphic%20details%20of%20the%20conditions%20in%20hospitals%2C%20how%20long%20they%20can%20function%2C%20and%20what%20will%20happen%20when%20they%20completely%20run%20out%20of%20standby%20fuel%20and%20generators.%20He%20said%20that%20could%20happen%20in%2048%20hours.%20That%20means%20many%20of%20the%20patients%20in%20those%20hospitals%20%E2%80%93%20and%20particularly%20young%20children%20%E2%80%93%20will%20face%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20slow%20painful%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20situation%20that%20children%20are%20facing%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20not%20been%20injured.%20He%20talks%20about%20the%20drastic%20shortage%20of%20clean%20water%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20children%20are%20now%20relying%20on%20brackish%20water%20or%20saline%20water%20from%20old%2C%20disused%20wells.%20The%20threat%20of%20a%20public%20health%20catastrophe%20is%20looming%20and%20getting%20closer%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20discussed%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20on%20children%E2%80%99s%20well-being%20and%20mental%20state%2C%20resulting%20from%20living%20under%20an%20Israeli%20blockade%20in%20Gaza%20since%202007-2008%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22