Power%20Plant%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Rampal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-border%20rail%20project%20near%20Tripura's%20capital%20Agartala%20and%20Akhaura%20in%20Bangladesh%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20cross-border%20trade%2C%20and%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Agartala%20and%20Kolkata%20via%20Dhaka.%20When%20fully%20completed%2C%20the%20cross-border%20rail%20link%20will%20cut%20the%20travel%20time%20from%20Kolkata%20to%20Agartala%20from%2036%20hours%20to%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20hailed%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Cross%20Border%20Rail%20Link%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20joy%20that%20we%20have%20come%20together%20again%20to%20celebrate%20the%20successful%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Our%20relationship%20is%20touching%20new%20highs.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20achieved%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20what%20has%20not%20been%20achieved%20in%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20are%20important%20for%20India's%20Look%20East%20Policy%20and%20will%20also%20boost%20connectivity%20to%20the%20northeast%20which%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20narrow%20Chicken's%20Neck%20or%20Siliguri%20Corridor.%20They%20are%20also%20a%20testament%20to%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20region%20around%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20with%20organizations%20like%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%C2%A0which%20has%20its%20secretariat%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'First%20Rail%20Link%20Between%20Northeast%2C%20Bangladesh'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala-Akhaura%20Rail%20Link%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20projects%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20pandemic%20with%20oxygen%20trains.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20rail%20link%20between%20the%20northeast%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20focused%20especially%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20connectivity%20and%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20bus%20services.%20We%20have%20connected%20Dhaka%2C%20Shillong%2C%20Agartala%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Kolkata.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20railway%20services.%20From%202020%2C%20we%20started%20container%20and%20parcel%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20Chittagong%20and%20the%20Mongla%20Port%2C%20we%20have%20connected%20the%20northeastern%20states%20of%20India.%20Our%20connectivity%20initiative%20worked%20as%20a%20lifeline%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20four%20new%20immigration%20check%20posts%20have%20been%20opened%20on%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20and%20our%20bilateral%20trade%20has%20nearly%20tripled.%20The%20journey%20of%20these%20nine%20years%20has%20made%20us%20reach%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala%20Akhaura%20Railway%20Link%20and%20it%20is%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'Firm%20Cooperation%20Between%20Countries'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20the%20relationship%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20is%20anchored%20in%20history%20culture%20language%20and%20both%20countries%20share%20values%20of%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20countless%20other%20commonalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Bangladesh%20attaches%20the%20highest%20importance%20to%20its%20relationship%20with%20India%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20She%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20government%2