n%20at%20the%20boy's%20head%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fman-allegedly-points-gun-6-year-old-left-halloween-goody-bag-wrong-hou-rcna123025%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20Nassau%20County%20Police%20Department%20were%20immediately%20notified%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20the%2043-year-old%20suspect%20was%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Wen's%20attorney%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20his%20client%20is%20presumed%20innocent.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20just%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%20He%20also%20asked%20the%20public%20to%20refrain%20from%20jumping%20to%20conclusions%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20the%20facts%20come%20out%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fman-arrested-pointing-gun-6-year-boys-head%2Fstory%3Fid%3D104532068%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident%20is%20currently%20ongoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-irony-is-that-elon-musk-after-tesla-wins-autopilot-trial-involving-fatal-crash-4535790%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Irony%20Is%20That...%26quot%3B%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20After%20Tesla%20Wins%20Autopilot%20Trial%20Involving%20Fatal%20Crash%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20comes%20amid%20a%20time%20when%20US%20is%20reeling%20under%20the%20uncontrolled%20and%20widespread%20use%20of%20guns%20across%20the%20country%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20country%20has%20recorded%20over%20500%20mass%20shootings%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gun%20Violence%20Archive%20(GVA)%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organization%20that%20defines%20a%20mass%20shooting%20as%20four%20or%20more%20people%20wounded%20or%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%