20angry%20mob%20also%20targeted%20an%20office%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20prompting%20the%20authorities%20to%20tighten%20the%20security%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecurity-increased-outside-houses-of-ministers-amid-maratha-quota-protests-4532254%5C%22%3EBeed%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Marathwada%20region%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20the%20renewed%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%5C%22%3Ewho%20chaired%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20the%20fresh%20wave%20of%20statewide%20protests%2C%20said%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota.%20Mr%20Shinde%20said%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20NCP%20veteran%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Ashok%20Chavan%20among%20others%20passed%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20to%20improve%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations%20is%20not%20new%20and%20the%20push%20for%20it%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20decades.%20Here%2C%20we%20chart%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20issue%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Did%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Protests%20Start%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarathas%2C%20who%20constitute%20nearly%2033%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20year%201981%20when%20the%20state%20saw%20its%20first%20protests%20demanding%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20been%20seeking%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20Marathas%20which%20will%20enable%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20for%20reservation.%20Kunbis%2C%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20agriculture%2C%20are%20grouped%20under%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20category%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20government%20brought%20an%20ordinance%20pronouncing%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20Marathas.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20gave%20its%20nod%20to%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20under%20a%20special%20provision%20in%202018-%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Class%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20Court%20Verdict%20In%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202019%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota.%20The%20court%20reduced%20it%20to%2012%20per%20cent%20in%20education%20and%2013%20per%20cent%20in%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20the%20provisions%20of%20Maharashtra%20law%20providing%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20which%20granted%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20for%20violating%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20quota%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%2010%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20turned%20down%20Maharashtra's%20government%20review%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20recent%20flare-ups%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20demanded%20that%20the%20centre%20resolve%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20by%20calling%20a%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698853860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgm7nqc7_maratha-protest-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-protests-a-timeline-of-long-drawn-political-legal-battle-eknath-shinde-meeting-4536331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fresh%20wave%20over%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20demand%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20once%20again%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20complex%20politics%20of%20the%20reservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-protests-a-timeline-of-long-drawn-political-legal-battle-eknath-shinde-meeting-4536331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-protests-a-timeline-of-long-drawn-political-legal-battle-eknath-shinde-meeting-4536331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-protests-a-timeline-of-long-drawn-political-legal-battle-eknath-shinde-meeting-4536331%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHo%20Sakta%20Hai...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit's%201st%20Official%20Update%20On%20Pandya's%20WC%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20player%20who%20provides%20balance%20to%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20unlike%20any%20other%20player.%20Top%20class%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%20is%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20one%20such%20player.%20He%20gave%20a%20good%20account%20of%20himself%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20matches%20th