g%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20n%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20also%20appealed%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20who%20is%20on%20hunger%20strike%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20since%20October%2025%2C%20to%20call%20off%20his%20fast%20and%20give%20the%20government%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20decided%20unanimously%20at%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20that%20the%20state%20should%20make%20efforts%20for%20securing%20Maratha%20reservation%20without%20touching%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities.%20I%20appeal%20and%20request%20Manoj%20Jarange%20to%20withdraw%20his%20fast%20and%20cooperate%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20state%20needs%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20curative%20petition%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20working%20on%20two%20fronts%20--%20issuing%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20to%20Marathas%20from%20Marathwada%20(so%20that%20they%20can%20avail%20of%20OBC%20reservation)%20and%20preparing%20an%20error-free%20submission%20as%20part%20of%20the%20curative%20petition%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20all-party%20meeting%20also%20expressed%20its%20disappointment%20over%20the%20violent%20incidents%20reported%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20Such%20violent%20acts%20would%20be%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20Maratha%20community's%20agitation%20for%20reservation.%20The%20state%20government%20needs%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%20a%20submission%20that%20will%20pass%20the%20legal%20test%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20is%20making%20honest%20efforts%20so%20that%20the%20Maratha%20community%20gets%20reservation%20benefits.%20The%20backward%20class%20commission%20is%20working%20on%20a%20war%20footing.%20The%20reservation%20given%20by%20the%20government%20w