0is%20that%20boys%20should%20work%20because%20they%20have%20a%20family%20to%20feed%2C%20while%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20a%20good-looking%20husband%20with%20a%20government%20job.%20But%20my%20brother%20changed%20this%20outlook%20and%20supported%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20job%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20inspired%20her%20to%20venture%20even%20further%20outside%20her%20comfort%20zone.%20She%20acquired%20the%20skills%20to%20effectively%20communicate%20with%20school%20principals%20about%20the%20value%20she%20gained%20from%20the%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20programmes%20of%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20and%20to%20persuade%20parents%20to%20enroll%20their%20daughters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPermission%20from%20parents%20is%20very%20difficult%20at%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20unsafe.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20win%20their%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20did%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidya%20was%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix%20female%20kabaddi%20coaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20ages%20(between%2023%20and%2025)%20who%20joined%20Magic%20Bus%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20other%20coaches%20were%20Komal%20Pachare%2C%20Nilam%20Verma%2C%20Shital%20Borkar%2C%20Poornima%20Chandekar%20and%20Reema%20Khushwah%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20common%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20empower%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20sports%2C%20just%20as%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20are%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20S