20article%20is%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289013%2Fthe-better-india-celebrates-unsung-sports-heroes%2F%5C%22%3E%23MakingSportWork%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20series%20launched%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20and%20Sports%20and%20Society%20Accelerator.%20The%20series%20celebrates%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20with%20stories%20of%20heroes%20who%20have%20spent%20years%20working%20to%20improve%20lives%20around%20them%20through%20sports.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20inspiring%20tales%20of%20those%20who%20are%20%23MakingSportWork.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGanga%20and%20Jamana%20are%20twin%20sisters%20who%20come%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Ratlam%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Their%20journey%20with%20sports%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one.%20Being%20residents%20of%20a%20conservative%20village%20in%20Ratlam%2C%20education%20was%20never%20a%20first%20choice%2C%20let%20alone%20indulging%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20relentless%20persuasion%2C%20which%20went%20on%20for%20six%20months%2C%20their%20parents%20allowed%20the%20twins%20to%20join%20the%20%3Cem%3ENanhi%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%20after-school%20tuition%20centre%20run%20by%20the%20Naandi%20Foundation%2C%20where%20they%20received%20daily%20academic%20support.%20Soon%2C%20they%20took%20this%20opportunity%20to%20play%20sports%2C%20which%20was%20a%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20demonstrated%20exceptional%20skill%20in%20sports%2C%20and%20were%20soon%20participating%20in%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20sports%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20began%20in%202019%20when%20Rohini%20Mukherjee%2C%20the%20then%20head%20of%20Nanhi%20Kali%20operations%2C%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20introduce%20the%20girls%20to%20sports.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20fundamental%20life%20skills%20that%20school%20classrooms%20can%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20%E2%80%93%20leadership%2C%20teamwork%2C%20facing%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20And%20that%20is%20where%20sports%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%201%2C90%2C000%20girls%2C%20including%20the%20twin%20sisters%2C%20get%20at%20least%2010%20years%20of%20schooling%20and%20are%20introduced%20to%20sports%20once%20they%20are%20enrolled%20in%20this%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%20In%20the%20current%20edition%20that%20started%20in%20August%202023%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20girls%20under%20their%20wing%20are%20competing%20right%20from%20the%20village%20level%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nationals%20organised%20by%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20organisation%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooked%20to%20introduce%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20challenge%20of%20not%20having%20anyone%20on%20the%20staff%20who%20could%20lead%20a%20sports-focused%20initiative.%20Fortunately%2C%20they%20found%20the%20right%20candidate%20in%20Lisa%20Murawsky%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20international%20sports%20consultant%2C%20educator%20and%20coach%20for%20over%2020%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohini%20(now%20the%20Head%20of%20Global%20Partnerships%20and%20Strategy)%20and%20Lisa%20together%20created%20the%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99%20programme%20for%20the%20foundation%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20these%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_59374552529518093