065-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-2-1698418065-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-2-1698418065-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-2-1698418065-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Michelle%20established%20a%20smart%20centre%20which%20is%20a%20free%20and%20inclusive%20play%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20years%2C%20she%20discovered%20the%20scams%20in%20the%20adoption%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20NGOs%20weren%E2%80%99t%20taking%20in%20orphans%20who%20lost%20both%20their%20parents%20because%20they%20had%20to%20%E2%80%98get%20rid%20of%E2%80%99%20them%20at%2018%20years%20of%20age%20when%20the%20government%20funding%20stops.%20They%20would%20prefer%20to%20take%20only%20those%20kids%20who%20have%20a%20single%20parent%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20a%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20orphanages%20were%20actually%20moonlighting%20as%20boarding%20schools%20for%20the%20poor%3B%20not%20working%20for%20the%20ones%20truly%20in%20need.%20They%20continued%20calling%20themselves%20orphanages%20so%20that%20they%20could%20rake%20in%20donations%20from%20benefactors%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reveals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20was%20thinking%20about%20the%20children.%20It%20was%20all%20about%20business%2C%20laws%2C%20and%20rules.%20Nobody%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20children%20and%20the%20more%20I%20saw%20that%2C%20the%20more%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20orphans%20without%20%E2%80%9Cconnections%E2%80%9D%20were%20housed%20in%20government%20institutions%20that%20lacked%20adequate%20amounts%20of%20food%2C%20medical%20care%2C%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20discussions%20amongst%20people%20and%20other%20NGOs%20about%20the%20orphaned%20children%2C%20I%20kept%20hearing%20that%20nothing%20could%20be%20really%20done%20as%20these%20children%20could%20never%20be%20like%20our%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Michelle%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20tell%20me%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%3B%20you%20can%20tell%20me%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20expensive%3B%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20tell%20me%20that%20nothing%20can%20be%20done.%20They%20are%20our%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20underscores%20strongly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333189%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid