%20out%20for%20the%20Gujarati%20flavours%20to%20shine%20through%20in%20every%20bowl.%20Krutarthsinh%20M%20Jadeja%E2%80%99s%2085-year-old%20mother%20receives%20the%20guests%20with%20garlands%2C%20applies%20a%20%3Cem%3Eteeka%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20their%20forehead%2C%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGod%20bless%20you.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20has%20always%20welcomed%20the%20guests.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20tradition.%20She%20says%20that%20we%20must%20pray%20and%20dine%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Krutarthsinh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20otherwise%20bleak%20Kutchi%20village%2C%20the%20sloped%20road%20bends%20to%20an%20arched%20gate%20fixed%20with%20iron%20nails.%20This%20was%20done%20to%20keep%20elephants%20and%20enemies%20from%20invading%20the%20property.%20Sitting%20on%20a%20mound%2C%20the%20small%20manor%20watches%20over%20the%20six%20generations%20that%20have%20lived%20here%20for%20118%20years.%20The%20bowed%20branches%20of%20Bougainvillea%20engulf%20the%20suites%20here%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejharokhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20sitting%20windows%20protruding%20outwards%20from%20a%20building)%20articulate%20heritage%20fervour%20even%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKrutarthsinh%2C%20the%20ever-smiling%20host%2C%20is%20now%20taking%20care%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329447%2Fdevra-homestay-in-udaipur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eancestral%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20historically%20known%20as%20the%20Darbargadh%20in%20Devpur%20village%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270912%2Fchaturbhuj-temple-in-gwalior-has-worlds-oldest-zero-symbol%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20km%20from%20Bhuj%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20now%20known%20commercially%20as%20the%20Devpur%20Homestay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20a%20few%20rooms%20sti